            {
              "content": "=Summarize the following news into a short daily briefing.\n\nRules:\n- Categorize into: Tech, Gaming, Business, World\n- Keep it under 200 words total\n- Only include important news\n- Make it clean and readable\n\nNews:\n{{ $json.news }}"
